  <thing id="cRG1Versat" name="Versatile Improvisation" description="[Monk of the Empty Hand]  As a swift action, the monk may cause his weapon, unarmed, or natural attacks to deal damage as if they were another type (bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing) for 1 round, regardless of the attack’s normal damage type." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
