  <thing id="cRG1ImpEva" name="Improved Evasion" description="The monk’s evasion ability improves. He still takes no damage on a successful Reflex saving throw against attacks, but henceforth he takes only half damage on a failed save. A helpless monk does not gain the benefit of improved evasion.  \n\nA monk must be at least 8th level and have the evasion edge to take improved evasion." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Take only half damage on a failed Reflex save." uniqueness="unique">
